y":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:15:44.000Z","msg":"138<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:16:13.000Z","msg":"玩咗十幾年唔係最尾先嚟咁樣爛尾呀"},{"pid":"9d0de4c2f2e9958f672e20892703e2b7188942cc","tid":2435714,"uid":86557,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7093ba94e1a839e117e3b2c993d21d7fee82ef0a","tid":2435714,"uid":299548,"like":56,"dislike":157,"score":-101,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"我屌呀 艾倫比邊個砍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c7ee3d89d7fdd3b8c30436f6b63d05ad779ba3","tid":2435714,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:12:36.000Z","msg":"病嬌真可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77185a2175727f0768ce4f0f04e53fe0b022ca40","tid":2435714,"uid":393935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4caffa42c53dd5dd0d65fe4180bf3fccad385e0","tid":2435714,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"印度男不滿女兒交男友直接斬首 「拎頭顱上街」去自首<br />\n<br />\n印度男子斬首17歲女兒後，拎著她的頭顱準備去自首。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n印度北方邦一名男子，本月3日手上卻拎著17歲女兒頭顱，大喇喇走上街頭，嚇壞當地居民<br />\n急著報警。男子宣稱，他是這名少女的父親，因為滿女兒的異性交友狀況，竟手持利器，在<br />\n房間一刀剁下女兒頭顱，還把斬首的頭顱直接拎上街頭。<br />\n綜合NDTV、印度時報報導，印度北方邦哈爾多伊一處村落，身穿淺色上衣的庫馬（SarveshK<br />\numar），看似平靜地走在大街上，但當地居民卻一陣恐慌，因為他手上拎著一顆少女頭顱準<br />\n備去自首，而死者是他17歲的親生女兒。<br />\n<br />\n警方獲報後趕到現場關切，並拿手機蒐證錄影。庫馬面對2名員警盤問，直接承認手上拎的<br />\n是親生女兒的頭顱，他因為不滿意女兒跟他不喜歡的年輕男性，關係太親密，一氣之下斬首<br />\n自己的女兒，他並當場承認「我關門上鎖就做了，屍體在房間。」<br />\n庫馬事後被帶回警局進行偵訊，但當地員警也被爆出，在與庫馬接觸時，竟也拎過這名遇害<br />\n少女的頭顱，目前這名不當拎著死者頭顱的員警，也已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3eeaidD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3eeaidD&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1nze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=6b2ed970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3eeaidD</a><br />\n<br />\n死印狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:56:05.000Z","msg":"頭抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7997aa7696d9619b76373ecd7d856a251820f71a","tid":2435714,"uid":128003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7093ba94e1a839e117e3b2c993d21d7fee82ef0a","tid":2435714,"uid":299548,"like":56,"dislike":157,"score":-101,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T21:08:10.000Z","msg":"仆你個街劇透"},{"pid":"d9346c106c8dc678589e7c1ece7799eca6e374e1","tid":2435714,"uid":25494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T22:38:58.000Z","msg":"乜巨人真係咁多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8b488ff8bfdb557e594c27a9aea3e1140f86af","tid":2435714,"uid":323551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e201ae9d9db98c46e964c35c46d25cb97f84ae64","tid":2435714,"uid":192078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"拿拿屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T22:44:12.000Z","msg":"拿屍理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb52a680a779e76325f54111a84c73dcf6855c","tid":2435714,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"79a6b2c2d72b40fcd77e67af28b485ff17a91bb7","tid":2435714,"uid":117689,"like":334,"dislike":2,"score":332,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T22:59:40.000Z","msg":"印度都有好錫個女嘅人嘅<br />\n諗起好耐以前俾個女嫌買唔到smart phone返學，走去自殺嘅農夫&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"803773042d9a16fc36a1e1d04fb501172e510421","tid":2435714,"uid":314611,"like":0,"di